{"word":"κατάκειμαι","slug":"κατάκειμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατάϰειμαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κεῖμαι\">κεῖμαι</a></el>] ‘be in a reclining posture’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> context signaling circumstance<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as an ill person <b>be abed, lie (sick) <a href='B:480 1:30'>Mk 1:30</a>; <a href='B:480 2:4'>2:4</a>; <a href='B:500 5:6'>J 5:6</a>; <a href='B:510 9:33'>Ac 9:33</a>; <a href='B:510 28:8'>28:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as a diner (reclining being common posture at mealtime) <b>recline</b> = <b>dine <a href='B:480 2:15'>Mk 2:15</a>; <a href='B:480 14:3'>14:3</a>; <a href='B:490 5:29'>Lk 5:29</a>; <a href='B:490 7:37'>7:37</a>; <a href='B:530 8:10'>1 Cor 8:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατακαυχῶ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κατακλάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}